title: This Historic 1 BR Apt Loft Can Be Yours Today. Don’t Wait!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'HURRY our rent-restricted apartments are going fast!', 'Submit your application paperwork quickly and easily today to reserve your new home.', 'Located in Uptown, Buzza Lofts offers beautiful one and two bedroom homes only minutes from countless dining, shopping, entertainment options.', 'Each home features an open floor-plan, large windows providing amazing natural light, and an in-home washer and dryer.', 'Residents enjoy the stellar amenities including a top-of-the-line fitness center, rooftop terrace, and courtyard veranda with a fire pit and BBQ grills.', 'Gas, water, sewer, and trash removal are included in rent.', 'Contact us today to schedule your tour!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Energy-Star Rated Stainless Steel Appliances - Modern & Environmentally Safe.', "- 12'-Foot Ceilings Give You A Sense Of Possession & Entitlement", '- Eco-Conscious Lighting, Heating & Water Flow Systems', '- Fitness Room Equipped With All The Latest In Gym Technology & Exercise Equipment - time', 'To Get Rid Of That Gym Membership Card!', '- Full-Size, In-Home Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home - No Need To Drag Your Dirty Laundry Around Town Anymore!', '- Professional & Courteous On-Site Management Team', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Buzza Lofts participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 12:00PM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Buzza Lofts of Uptown', '1006 West Lake Street', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55408', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'Dqru2fThq']
